#: exhibition.php:132
msgid ""
"The string of creation has vibrated the membrane, each resonance weaving the "
"warp and weft of spacetime thoughts."
msgstr ""
"La corde de la création a fait vibrer la membrane, chaque résonance tissant "
"la chaîne et la trame des pensées de l'espace-temps."

#: exhibition.php:139
msgid "Silver Blogger"
msgstr "Blogueur d'argent"

#: exhibition.php:144
msgid ""
"The wheel of creation has engaged the gears, each component calibrating the "
"temporal precision of your blog."
msgstr ""
"La roue de la création s'est enclenchée, chaque élément calibrant la "
"précision temporelle de votre blog."

#: exhibition.php:145 exhibition.php:158
#, php-format
msgid "%s more days to next level"
msgstr "%s jours supplémentaires pour le niveau suivant"

#: exhibition.php:152
msgid "Bronze Blogger"
msgstr "Blogueur de bronze"

#: exhibition.php:157
msgid ""
"The ship of creation has set sail, each wave carving the depth markers of "
"your blog's journey."
msgstr ""
"Le navire de la création a pris le large, chaque vague creusant les "
"marqueurs de profondeur du voyage de votre blog."

#: exhibition.php:175
msgid "Gold Popularity"
msgstr "Popularité de l'or"

#: exhibition.php:180
msgid ""
"You have planted a garden of wisdom, its fragrance now discovered by distant "
"butterflies."
msgstr ""
"Vous avez planté un jardin de sagesse, dont les papillons lointains "
"découvrent maintenant le parfum."

#: exhibition.php:187
msgid "Silver Popularity"
msgstr "Popularité de l'argent"

#: exhibition.php:192
msgid ""
"You have illuminated the star chart of reading, each piece of writing "
"flowing through the galaxy."
msgstr ""
"Vous avez illuminé la carte stellaire de la lecture, chaque écrit circulant "
"dans la galaxie."

#: exhibition.php:193 exhibition.php:206
#, php-format
msgid "%s more visits to next level"
msgstr "%s plus de visites au niveau suivant"

#: exhibition.php:200
msgid "Bronze Popularity"
msgstr "Popularité du bronze"

#: exhibition.php:205
msgid ""
"You have built a harbor of knowledge, the ripples of thought continuously "
"spreading."
msgstr ""
"Vous avez construit un port de connaissances, dont les ondes de pensée se "
"propagent continuellement."

#: exhibition.php:223
msgid "Gold Friendship"
msgstr "Amitié en or"

#: exhibition.php:228
msgid ""
"The world of friendship has no boundaries, the starry river will mark your "
"position."
msgstr ""
"Le monde de l'amitié n'a pas de frontières, la rivière étoilée marquera "
"votre position."

#: exhibition.php:235
msgid "Silver Friendship"
msgstr "Amitié en argent"

#: exhibition.php:240
msgid ""
"The network of friendship has been laid out, each resonance will eventually "
"echo."
msgstr ""
"Le réseau d'amitié a été mis en place, chaque résonance finira par se "
"répercuter."

#: exhibition.php:241 exhibition.php:254
#, php-format
msgid "%s more links to next level"
msgstr "%s plus de liens vers le niveau suivant"

#: exhibition.php:248
msgid "Bronze Friendship"
msgstr "Amitié en bronze"

#: exhibition.php:253
msgid ""
"The journey of making friends has just begun, each encounter marks a new "
"chapter."
msgstr ""
"Le voyage pour se faire des amis ne fait que commencer, chaque rencontre "
"marque un nouveau chapitre."

#: exhibition.php:271
msgid "Gold Author"
msgstr "AuteurAuteur de l'or"

#: exhibition.php:276
msgid ""
"The power of words has blossomed in your hands, rich creations have gathered "
"into an ocean."
msgstr ""
"Le pouvoir des mots s'est épanoui entre vos mains, de riches créations se "
"sont rassemblées en un océan."

#: exhibition.php:283
msgid "Silver Author"
msgstr "AuteurAuteur de l'argent"

#: exhibition.php:288
msgid ""
"You have woven an extensive web of thoughts, the streams of inspiration are "
"rushing into rivers."
msgstr ""
"Vous avez tissé une vaste toile de pensées, les ruisseaux d'inspiration se "
"transforment en rivières."

#: exhibition.php:289 exhibition.php:302
#, php-format
msgid "%s more words to next level"
msgstr "%s mots supplémentaires au niveau suivant"

#: exhibition.php:296
msgid "Bronze Author"
msgstr "Auteur de bronze"

#: exhibition.php:301
msgid ""
"Sparks of words dance at your fingertips, as the faint light of thoughts "
"quietly illuminates."
msgstr ""
"Des étincelles de mots dansent au bout de vos doigts, tandis que la faible "
"lumière des pensées s'illumine tranquillement."

#: exhibition.php:438
